<p class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Sunnyside </strong>&#8211; In collaboration with Morag Myerscough (UK), Jenna co-created a series of vibrant flags displayed around Ballarat, including a transformative textile installation in Hop Lane.&nbsp;<em>Karndorr (Tracks)</em>&nbsp;reflects Wadawurrung Sky Country through bold colours and cultural storytelling. Jenna also led a Colour and Storytelling workshop, where participants explored patterns and forms to create expressive pieces rooted in Wadawurrung heritage, deepening their connection to both culture <span class="noWidow">and community.</span></p>


