<p class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Deep Listening Project</strong>, <strong>Craft Lab</strong> &#8211; a First Nations–led project that explores Ballarat’s past and present through the voices of its Aboriginal community. Working across the themes of&nbsp;<strong>HEALING, HEART, HISTORY, STORY, SONG and SPIRIT</strong>, Jenna created culturally safe spaces for community members to share their experiences and help shape each artwork. The resulting six installations formed the entry to the Craft Lab activation at the historic Mining Exchange—inviting visitors to walk through the stories of <span class="noWidow">Wadawurrung Country.</span></p>


