<p class="has-text-align-center is-style-constrained-paragraph"><strong>Ballarat Begonia Festival Letters</strong> &#8211; Each of the letters represents a different native plant blending the beauty of begonias with the rich diversity of our natural landscape. An opportunity to educate and inspire community to learn more about the beautiful Wadawurrung culture that <span class="noWidow">surrounds us.</span></p>


