<p class="has-text-align-center is-style-constrained-paragraph"><strong>Ballarat Heritage Festival</strong> &#8211; A shipping container transformed into a fully immersive experience, telling the Wadawurrung dreamtime story of Bonan Youang (Mount Buninyong) and Terrinalum (Mount Elephant). Visitors were able to step into the fully transformed immersive display, featuring audio and visual storytelling, sensory boxes and original artworks all created by myself, as part of the visual and <span class="noWidow">sensory experience.</span></p>


