<p class="has-text-align-center is-style-constrained-paragraph"><strong>Sexual Health Victoria</strong> &#8211; <em>Kolingwadangitj (All Walk Together) –</em> This custom commission created for Sexual Health Victoria was a deeply meaningful work that celebrated the strength, wisdom, and cultural significance of both men’s and women’s business. It honoured the vital roles each played in advancing sexual health education and overall wellbeing, while acknowledging the knowledge systems that guide these practices. At its heart, the artwork served as a reminder that everyone has a part to play in fostering safe, informed, and supportive spaces for individuals and <span class="noWidow">communities alike.</span></p>


