<p class="has-text-align-center is-style-constrained-paragraph"><strong>White Night Ballarat </strong>&#8211; <em>Koki Bundjil (Brother Bundjil)</em> &#8211; An original artwork (inspired by my own kinship guide &#8211; my brother) transformed into a large inflatable, lit up to fly high over Wadawurrung Country on <span class="noWidow">the night. </span></p>


